{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Sosh theme is the theme dedicated to the Sosh brand only."}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"metadata":{"role":"collection","symbolKind":"module","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_sosh.png"}],"roleHeading":"Library","modules":[{"name":"Theme Sosh"}],"externalID":"OUDSThemesSosh","title":"Theme Sosh"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesSosh\/documentation\/OUDSThemesSosh"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"code":["🧬 Theme version: 2.3.0"],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This is the Sosh theme any Sosh product must use, and cannot be subclassed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It embeds also in its target the Sosh brand colors which are not shared nor exposed in lower level targets or outside any module not depending to it.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In other words, this ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesSosh\/documentation\/OUDSThemesSosh\/SoshTheme","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is based on the abstract "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":", uses all the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}]},{"text":" kit and brings the Sosh brand colors and assets.","type":"text"}]},{"name":"Tip","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This theme embeds and registers the fonts for the Sosh theme, you just need to use the theme object as is.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"tip"},{"name":"Important","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Sosh theme does not embed colors for charts yet and is read only: it cannot be subclassed or derivated","type":"text"}]}],"style":"important"},{"level":2,"text":"How to use the t